WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Hello and welcome to this documentary
about marine life.

2
00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:09.800
The ocean covers over 70 percent
of our planet.

3
00:00:10.200 --> 00:00:18.500
It is home to millions of species,
many of which remain undiscovered.

4
00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:25.300
In this episode, we will explore
the coral reefs of the Pacific.

5
00:00:25.800 --> 00:00:30.500
These ecosystems support an incredible
diversity of life.
